author: sandakith
msg: On the annotated pojo the name was picked up by name attribute of the javax.jws.WebService annotation now but
JSR 181 specifies that the in javax.jws.WebService the parameter serviceName contains the wsdl:service name
to mapp. If its not available then the default will be Simple name of the class + "Service"
Now moved the logic was moved to a Util method and it will return the  String version of the ServiceName according to the JSR 181 spec

msg: Fix erratic behaviour when filters were used with Perl 5.10.
